(306, '探秘地球“蓝色领土”—中国科学院学趣海洋生物科普探索', '探秘地球“蓝色领土”—中国科学院学趣海洋生物科普探索', '<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">深蓝色背景下</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><?xml:namespace prefix = \"o\" ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">一幕幕的情景剧上演着</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">上演着《海底总动员》小丑鱼父亲逆流而上寻找儿子尼莫</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">上演着安徒生的小美人鱼为见王子放弃美妙歌声</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">上演着鲨鱼家族的黑帮故事</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">上演着海明威的《老人与海》……</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">那一片深蓝是地球的“蓝色领土”——海洋，占据着地球表面四分之三的面积。在这一片深蓝色中有着许多人类未知的秘密，带着这些疑问，今年<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">8</FONT><FONT face=宋体>月，中国科学院行政管理局科学文化传播中心带你探秘地球神秘的“蓝色领土”。此次海洋夏令营不仅让你认识海洋及其生物，还带你采集制作属于你自己的海洋生物标本。今夏，在世界帆船之都——青岛，我们海边赶海，登山赏石，品尝特色农家宴，畅游海水浴场，共度美好时光。</FONT></SPAN></P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p><IMG style=\"HEIGHT: 249px; WIDTH: 349px\" src=\"http://www.xuequ360.com/editor/uploadfile/201406091402295846.jpg\" width=382 height=272></o:p></SPAN></P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">活动支持单位：中国科学院动物研究所</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">活动时间：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">2014<FONT face=宋体>年</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">8</FONT><FONT face=宋体>月</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">6</FONT><FONT face=宋体>日</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">-10</FONT><FONT face=宋体>日</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><STRONG>适合年龄：</STRONG>6-12岁（家长陪同）</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">活动地点：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">山东青岛</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">活动内容：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">一、参观青岛海洋所，认识各种海洋生物（贝壳海螺为主）。二、清理及制作贝类标本。三、采集和分类海洋生物标本。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">活动名额：不少于<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">20</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人（人数不足</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">20</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人活动取消）</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">活动费用：<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3580</FONT><FONT face=宋体>元</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">/</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人（学生需带学生证）（家长和孩子价格相同）</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=p0 style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P