(312, '深山猎奇—京郊松山昆虫捕捉与辨识亲子体验之旅', '深山猎奇—京郊松山昆虫捕捉与辨识亲子体验之旅', '<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /--><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">小小猎人松山行，大展拳脚捕昆虫。亲子上阵不惧怕，满载而归拍手庆。两天的时间里中科院老师带领大家在松山国家森林公园学习昆虫知识，诱捕昆虫，体验一次前所未有的昆虫猎人之旅。</font></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><br></span><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;扔掉PAD，拿起捕虫网，</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">这个周末与中科院老师朝夕相处，将会让你陶醉于种类繁多的昆虫世界，让你感受科学的趣味和魅力，培养你浓厚的科学兴趣，激励你主动的科学探索精神。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"></font></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; COLOR: rgb(68,68,68); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;松山的动物资源</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Tahoma\'; COLOR: rgb(68,68,68); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255)\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\'; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">松山自然保护区内的自然环境比较复杂，植被状况良好，落差高达1400多米的海拔变化为野生动物的生存繁衍创造了适宜的条件。动物区系组成以古北界种类为主，东洋界的种类占少数。截至2013年，统计得知保护区内共有脊椎动物68科216种及亚种，其中兽类15科29种，鸟类44科158种及亚种，爬行类5科15种，两栖类2科2种，鱼类2科12种。国家一级保护动物有金钱豹、金雕、白肩雕、黑鹳。</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\'; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255)\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\'; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">在松山，各种鸟类、鱼类、蛙、松鼠和蝴蝶是最为常见的野生动物，它们常常出现在游道的周围。然而，一些较大的哺乳动物却十分难得见到，它们往往出没在深山少有人类活动的核心区。2005年，松山保护区的工作人员在保护区内发现了金钱豹活动的足迹，这说明这种凶猛的哺乳动物有可能再次回到了松山。</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\'; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255)\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\'; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">此外，松山还蕴藏有丰富种类的昆虫，截至2013年，经调查，保护区共有昆虫多达16目98科540种。</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255)\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">我们捕虫的地方在这附近的兰角沟，昆虫多样。</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><!--EndFragment--><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><img src=\"http://www.xuequ360.com/editor/uploadfile/201407111405065961.jpg\"></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">上图：热闹的捕虫现场</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">专家简介<font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">：刘晔</font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><img src=\"http://www.xuequ360.com/editor/uploadfile/201407111405067039.jpg\"></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;<span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 28px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">计算机学士，昆虫学硕士。</span><br style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 28px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 28px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; DISPLAY: inline !important; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; FLOAT: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 现为中国科学院动物研究所研究人员。</span><br style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 28px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-VARIANT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 28px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></font></font></o:p></span></p><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 6px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 28px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 6px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"left\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">现为北京大学附属中学，北京理工大学课外指导老师。</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 6px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 28px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 6px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"left\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">科学家园网站特邀专家，三峡昆虫网管理员，中国昆虫爱好者论坛版主<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 主要研究昆虫分类学，并且正在从事中国步甲科昆虫的研究。</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 6px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 28px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 6px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"left\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">至今独立发现中国新种昆虫5种：圆胸齿青步甲，毛颊齿青步甲，川跗青步甲，滇跗青步甲，林氏跗青步甲，均发表于国外权威刊物。还有采到了一种锹甲新种，被其他昆虫学家命名为刘氏深山锹甲。</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 6px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 28px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 6px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"left\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">另外从事昆虫分类学设备的研发和推广，多次为中科院动物研究所和贵州大学讲解昆虫标本摄影及绘图讲座。</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 6px; WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 28px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 14px/28px 宋体; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 6px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"left\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">目前已在国外学术刊物发表文章4篇，在国内发表科普文章数余篇，多次为《知识就是力量》杂志撰写昆虫科普文章。参编学术和科普书籍4部。为科普畅销书《中国昆虫生态大图鉴》的副主编之一。</font><br></p></font>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">活动地区虫类分布：步甲、象甲、叶甲、蝴蝶、蛾类、蜻蜓、螳螂、天牛；其他动物：蜘蛛、蜥蜴、马陆</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;<img style=\"WIDTH: 500px; HEIGHT: 311px\" src=\"http://www.xuequ360.com/editor/uploadfile/201407111405066116.jpg\"></font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></span><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">考察时间：8月8日-9日已报满（周六、日）</span></font></p><p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 8月16日-17日</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-AUTOSPACE: \" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">考察地点：延庆县松山国家森林公园</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-AUTOSPACE: \" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"F