之旅，</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">踏上归途，辅导员与营员们挥手告别，满载收获和希望，登上回家的旅途。</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"><o:p><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://www.xuequ360.com/editor/uploadfile/201407111405066366.jpg\"></font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span>精彩瞬间：</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(255,0,0); FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">注意事项：</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 21pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-AUTOSPACE: \" class=\"p0\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">1.第一天集合地点</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">为中国科学院行政管理局大门口</span><span style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: 