 TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 5px 0px; FONT: 16px sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,0)\"><STRONG>第二天上午：</STRONG></SPAN>早餐后返程，结束愉快的天文科普之旅</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 5px 0px; FONT: 16px sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,0)\"><STRONG>◆本活动适合6-12岁小朋友参加；</STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 5px 0px; FONT: 16px sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,0,0)\"><STRONG>◆活动精彩照片</STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 5px 0px; FONT: 16px sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><IMG style=\"WIDTH: 500px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; FLOAT: none; HEIGHT: 418px\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/JRaHicnSujdGUzsgkQN0lxibngX8JL2ribChEhz6iaNgDwqq2sz0HlISa4FvMpibVuIW1TKKG63Nwgp8zScpOib0xwRw/0\" _src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/JRaHicnSujdGUzsgkQN0lxibngX8JL2ribChEhz6iaNgDwqq2sz0HlISa4FvMpibVuIW1TKKG63Nwgp8zScpOib0xwRw/0\" data-w=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8359683794466403\" data-s=\"300,640\"></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 5px 0px; FONT: 16px sans-serif; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><IMG style=\"WIDTH: 500px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; FLOAT: none; HEIGHT: 411px\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/JRaHicnSujdGUzsgkQN0lxibngX8JL2ribCvTOQSxibxNdHrhxnWVhr0NibReZia4YJU6QCbIvkWUuicIrv54TB0O0shA/0\" _src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/JRaHicnSujdGUzsgkQN0lxibngX8JL2ribCvTOQSxibxNdHrhxnWVhr0NibReZia4YJU6QCbIvkWUuicIrv54TB0O0shA